 {"id":"bd-35xyt","title":"Implement tmux environment detection","description":"Implement tmux environment detection.

## Fields

- binary_path: Path to actual tmux binary
- version: tmux version string
- shell_alias_detected: bool - shell has tmux alias/plugin
- recommended_path: /usr/bin/tmux (always)

## Detection Logic

```bash
# Find actual binary
which tmux           # May return alias
/usr/bin/tmux -V     # Always works

# Detect shell alias
type tmux            # Shows if function/alias
```

## Shell Plugin Detection

Check for common plugins that wrap tmux:
- oh-my-zsh tmux plugin
- tmuxinator
- tmux-resurrect

## Warning Behavior

If shell_alias_detected=true, include warning in output:
```json
{
  "tmux": {
    "shell_alias_detected": true,
    "warning": "Use binary_path to avoid shell plugin interference"
  }
}
```","status":"closed","priority":2,"issue_type":"task","created_at":"2026-01-19T23:29:12.071097787Z","created_by":"ubuntu","updated_at":"2026-01-20T06:38:37.177764435Z","closed_at":"2026-01-20T06:38:28.755198779Z","close_reason":"Implemented tmux environment detection in internal/robot/env.go with comprehensive tests in env_test.go. Features: findTmuxBinaryPath (standard paths + fallback), getTmuxVersion, detectTmuxAlias (shell function/alias detection), detectOhMyZshTmuxPlugin, detectTmuxinator, detectTmuxResurrect. Also added supporting types: TmuxEnvInfo, EnvOutput, SessionStructureInfo, ShellEnvInfo, TimingInfo, TargetingInfo. 28 tests pass.","compaction_level":0,"original_size":0,"dependencies":[{"issue_id":"bd-35xyt","depends_on_id":"bd-18gwh","type":"parent-child","created_at":"2026-01-30T23:34:28Z","created_by":"import"}]}
